inputs.input_value: Generate test cases for fund transfer

data.text:
Test Case ID: TC_FT_001
Title: Verify successful fund transfer within daily limit
Preconditions: User is logged in with an active account and has sufficient balance
Steps:
1. Navigate to Fund Transfer
2. Enter beneficiary details
3. Enter amount within daily limit
4. Submit transaction
5. Enter OTP sent to registered mobile number
Expected Result: Transaction completes successfully and confirmation is shown

Test Case ID: TC_FT_002
Title: Verify fund transfer failure due to insufficient balance
Preconditions: User is logged in with an active account and has insufficient balance
Steps:
1. Navigate to Fund Transfer
2. Enter beneficiary details
3. Enter amount exceeding available balance
4. Submit transaction
Expected Result: Error message is displayed indicating insufficient balance

Test Case ID: TC_FT_003
Title: Verify fund transfer validation error for invalid beneficiary details
Preconditions: User is logged in with an active account and has sufficient balance
Steps:
1. Navigate to Fund Transfer
2. Enter invalid beneficiary details
3. Enter amount within daily limit
4. Submit transaction
Expected Result: Error message is displayed indicating invalid beneficiary details

Test Case ID: TC_FT_004
Title: Verify fund transfer failure due to daily limit exceedance
Preconditions: User is logged in with an active account and has sufficient balance
Steps:
1. Navigate to Fund Transfer
2. Enter beneficiary details
3. Enter amount exceeding daily limit
4. Submit transaction
Expected Result: Error message is displayed indicating daily limit exceedance

Test Case ID: TC_FT_005
Title: Verify fund transfer failure due to OTP authentication failure
Preconditions: User is logged in with an active account and has sufficient balance
Steps:
1. Navigate to Fund Transfer
2. Enter beneficiary details
3. Enter amount within daily limit
4. Submit transaction
5. Enter incorrect OTP
Expected Result: Error message is displayed indicating OTP authentication failure
